1
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:44,039
Dad

2
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,439
You're finally awake

3
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:48,359
Dr. Wang

4
00:00:49,159 --> 00:00:50,399
My husband's condition...

5
00:00:50,399 --> 00:00:51,240
How bad is it?

6
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:52,679
Is he getting better?

7
00:00:52,679 --> 00:00:55,039
Director Lin is conscious now

8
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,200
but his bodily functions haven't recovered yet

9
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,719
Right now, he can't speak

10
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,439
His limbs, even his fingers, can't move

11
00:01:00,719 --> 00:01:02,439
We suspect a brain nerve injury

12
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,520
As for the specifics,

13
00:01:03,679 --> 00:01:05,120
we'll need more tests to know

14
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,599
But waking up is a very good sign

15
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:09,319
I believe he'll recover bit by bit

16
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:10,640
Try not to worry too much

17
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:12,079
He'll get better slowly

18
00:01:14,719 --> 00:01:15,239
Okay

19
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,719
Thank you, Dr. Wang

20
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:17,879
It's my job

21
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,280
I'll be going now

22
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:23,400
I'll bring Director Lin in for tests tomorrow

23
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,040
Okay, I'll see you out, Dr. Wang

24
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,680
Don't worry, Dad

25
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,640
You'll be better soon

26
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,000
I know, I know

27
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:48,760
How could I not worry?

28
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,040
He's awake

29
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,200
No, it's just...

30
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,040
He still can't move or speak

31
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:01,879
But the doctor said he'll recover soon

32
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,640
What if he ends up...

33
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:06,680
What are you doing? You didn't even make a sound!

34
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,599
You scared me to death

35
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,280
If you've done nothing wrong, what are you afraid of?

36
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,879
Hello? Hello?

37
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:11,759
What's wrong?

38
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,840
My dad is awake

39
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,759
I'm gonna tell him all the filthy things

40
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,680
you and Jiang Min did

41
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,599
You won't stay smug for much longer

42
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,080
Siqi, your dad just woke up

43
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,680
He hasn't fully recovered yet

44
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,159
If you tell him all that right now,

45
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,719
and his condition worsens,

46
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,120
won't it do more harm than good?

47
00:02:34,199 --> 00:02:34,800
Shut up

48
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,479
You just don't want my dad to get better

49
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:39,199
Siqi

50
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,039
I know you hate me

51
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,319
You want to kick me out of the Lin family

52
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:44,439
But, Siqi...

53
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,240
If you really care about your dad,

54
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:49,319
you shouldn't tell him this now

55
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,560
What you should do is make him happy

56
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,759
Keep his spirits up

57
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,879
That's how he'll recover faster

58
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,439
I'll let you off for now

59
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:00,360
But you'd better play your part

60
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,120
When my dad fully recovers,

61
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,680
I'll settle the score with you

62
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,800
You're awake

63
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,159
Why didn't you just stay asleep?

64
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:41,280
Then you could've kept your life

65
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,719
Uncle Sheng, what are you doing here?

66
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,000
I heard your dad woke up

67
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:02,719
So I came to see him

68
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,360
Is that more comfortable?

69
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,280
Thanks, Uncle Sheng. I'll do it

70
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:18,720
What's wrong, Dad? Are you uncomfortable?

71
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:27,920
Your dad can't move or talk

72
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,720
We need to be extra careful caring for him

73
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,759
Try to keep him as comfortable as possible

74
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,480
You're right

75
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,480
I'll be going now

76
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,360
I'll come back

77
00:04:41,439 --> 00:04:41,959
to see you next time

78
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:47,639
Thank you, Uncle Sheng

79
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,040
Bye-bye

80
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:13,959
Siqi

81
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,439
I came to see you

82
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,120
and Uncle Lin

83
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,399
Thanks

84
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,519
They're so pretty

85
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,480
But how did you know

86
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,040
I like pink peonies?

87
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:38,639
I figured you girls

88
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,800
all like this kind of flower

89
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,360
How is Uncle Lin doing?

90
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,920
He's awake

91
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,160
But he can't speak or move

92
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,319
Don't rush it

93
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,040
Got it

94
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,560
Oh, right

95
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,480
Your dad came by last night

96
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,839
Uncle Lin needs care right now

97
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,079
I was worried you'd be overwhelmed

98
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:07,720
So I looked it up online

99
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,279
For cases like his,

100
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:11,040
to prevent poor blood circulation

101
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:11,959
and muscle atrophy,

102
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,279
you need to massage him like this often

103
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,399
to stimulate his nerves

104
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:24,480
Thank you, Sheng Yuanzhou

105
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,959
If it weren't for you these past days,

106
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,279
I wouldn't know what to do

107
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,319
It's okay

108
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:30,800
Here, you try

109
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:41,160
I think my dad moved

110
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,639
I think he really moved

111
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,279
Uncle, try moving again

112
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,000
He really moved!

113
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:50,480
I'll go get the doctor

114
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,560
Now he can even move his fingers

115
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,920
If he can talk in a couple days,

116
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,160
that damn girl Lin Siqi

117
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,639
will definitely report us

118
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,600
Lin Chengren will definitely divorce me

119
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,399
Don't panic

120
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,240
He's not fully recovered yet, is he?

121
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,639
We still have time

122
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:14,560
How about we leave?

123
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,279
Leave?

124
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,720
Leave for where?

125
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,120
Even if we leave,

126
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:19,160
what about afterward?

127
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:19,920
Then here's what we'll do

128
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,279
While I can still call the shots in the Lin family

129
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,240
We'll sell off every asset we can

130
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,079
Calm down first

131
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:26,240
Even if he really wakes up

132
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,399
and finds out about us,

133
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:28,720
you're the mother of his two sons

134
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,639
He has to think of the children

135
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,800
He won't throw you out

136
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,480
Think of the children?

137
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:35,959
The kids aren't even his

138
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,759
What did you say?

139
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,199
The kids are yours

140
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,639
Then you can never say it, no matter what

141
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,399
Of course I won't

142
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:51,040
Am I crazy?

143
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,839
I'm just afraid that damn Lin Siqi

144
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:53,600
will investigate

145
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,680
You don't know how crafty she is

146
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:56,399
If she ends up...

147
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,560
There won't be any ifs

148
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,600
When did you get here?

149
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:08,160
Either way, I've heard everything I needed to

150
00:08:08,439 --> 00:08:09,399
The Lin family's money...

151
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,399
You won't get a single cent of it

152
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,120
And starting today,

153
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,600
you two

154
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:16,639
are getting the hell out of this house

155
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,920
Otherwise,

156
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:20,000
I'll take my two younger brothers to get a

157
00:08:20,839 --> 00:08:22,759
paternity test

158
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:28,000
Chairman Sheng, you have to help me this time

159
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,839
We're in the same boat

160
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:31,680
If Lin Chengren really wakes up,

161
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,240
you'll be...

162
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,759
I'll be what?

163
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,919
Of course you'll be fine

164
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,360
I mean,

165
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:41,840
I saw it clearly at the scene that day

166
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,639
Lin Chengren fell on his own

167
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,279
I'm just worried if he really wakes up,

168
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,519
he'll bring us unnecessary trouble

169
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,600
Mrs. Lin

170
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,200
As long as you keep your mouth shut,

171
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,960
we'll get through this safely

172
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,399
I understand

173
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,879
Thank you

174
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,279
for coming back with me to get my things

175
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,399
No need to be so polite with me

176
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,480
I hope when my dad sees these things,

177
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,200
he'll recover much faster

178
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,279
Didn't the doctor say so?

179
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,639
It'll definitely be fine

180
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,120
Breakdance Competition Champion

181
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,440
My dad won it when he was in college

182
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,559
He's been bragging about it ever since

183
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,600
I didn't think Uncle Lin was so cool

184
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,320
Everyone was young once

185
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:35,919
True

186
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,519
How old were you in this one?

187
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,559
About six

188
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,360
So cute

189
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,639
Dad

190
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:58,440
You have to get better soon

191
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:02,360
Why are you back again?

192
00:10:04,039 --> 00:10:06,039
I was worried you'd get hungry keeping watch,

193
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,519
so I bought some snacks for you

194
00:10:07,879 --> 00:10:08,559
Thanks

195
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,320
Uncle Lin is moving a lot more than this morning

196
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,279
Don't you think that's a little weird?

197
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:24,679
What is it?

198
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,320
Uncle Lin's hand

199
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,919
keeps drawing vertical lines

200
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:31,039
It looks like he's writing numbers

201
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,039
Numbers?

202
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,679
Look

203
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:37,759
One

204
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:39,279
One

205
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:40,600
One

206
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,000
Are you writing the number One One One, Uncle Lin?

207
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,879
Maybe my dad can only draw vertical lines now?

208
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,080
Uncle Lin just responded to me

209
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:48,919
What?

210
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:50,519
He closed his eyes just now

211
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,279
He did?

212
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,639
I'll ask again

213
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:56,720
If you're writing the number One One One,

214
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,159
then close your eyes one more time

215
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:00,159
Look!

216
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,759
One One One

217
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,200
What does One One One mean?

218
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,200
Found it

219
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,519
What?

220
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,720
One One One

221
00:11:28,799 --> 00:11:29,960
Bai Zimei

222
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,159
She's your mom

223
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,240
How could this be here?

224
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:40,480
So my dad's been guiding us the whole time

225
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,200
to find One One One

226
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:42,720
It was so we'd

227
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,080
find your mom's medical record

228
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,720
Could it be...

229
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,120
this has something to do with Sheng Shizhong

230
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,600
not letting anyone mention Bai Zimei?

231
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,559
Bai Zimei said the Sheng Shizhong now

232
00:12:02,559 --> 00:12:03,559
isn't her husband,

233
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:05,279
but the driver, Hu Jin

234
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:07,000
Hu Jin used the Key of Fate

235
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,240
to become Sheng Shizhong
